{"id": 527, "date": "1987-02-24T11:00:25", "date_gmt": "1987-02-24T19:00:25", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=527"}, "modified": "2026-06-09T10:22:52", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-09T17:22:52", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-levon-helms-all-stars-up-on-cripple-creek", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/02/24/meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-levon-helms-all-stars-up-on-cripple-creek/", "title": {"rendered": "Up on Cripple Creek"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>On August 22, 1987, Bruce made a guest appearance with Levon Helm&#8217;s All -Stars at The Stone Pony on August 22, 1987, and in addition to a rocking cover of &#8220;Lucille,&#8221; they just\u00a0<em>had</em> to play one of The Band&#8217;s greatest hits.</p>\n<p>Take a listen:</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-527-14\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/01-Up-On-Cripple-Creek-online-audio-converter.com_.mp3?_=14\" /><a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/01-Up-On-Cripple-Creek-online-audio-converter.com_.mp3\">http://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/01-Up-On-Cripple-Creek-online-audio-converter.com_.mp3</a></audio>\n<div id=\"v-8mnXClx5-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/8mnXClx5?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p>And of course, here&#8217;s the original by The Band from way back in 1969.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kBGSf9kViEY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>Up on Cripple Creek</strong><br />\n<strong>First performed:</strong> August 22, 1987 (Asbury Park, NJ)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> April 21, 2017 (Asbury Park, NJ)</p>\n<p>\u00a9 January 29, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Get (very) up close and personal as Bruce and Levon Helm&#8217;s All-Stars play &#8220;Up on Cripple Creek&#8221; at The Stone Pony on August 22, 1987.\u00a0</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69777, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_feature_clip_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [3617, 5], "tags": [253, 11, 2272, 